General Information

Wotnot multi-purpose biodegradable bags are made using gmo-free corn starch and come in two convenient rolls of 25. Comply with European and American standards for biodegradability.

Warnings

Keep out of reach of children. Do not flush. For external use only.

Common Uses

Multi-purpose biodegradable bags in 2 convenient rolls of 25. Use for disposing nappy, dog waste, food waste & sanitary products.

Ingredients

GMO Free Corn Starch

Directions

Use a multi-purpose biodegradable bag for disposing nappy, dog waste, food waste & sanitary products.
